<HEAD>NICOSIA: and Egypt.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   IRNA said the Foreign Ministry decision to sever ties was
announced at 11.30 a.m., ``exactly the same time the Majlis
(parliament) last Tuesday decided to give Britain seven days to
decide over the matter.''
   The agency, quoted a Foreign Ministry statement as saying: ``The
world oppressors and the West which find genuine Islam against their
